tps://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557", "stars": 951, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 516313, "username": "linuxgo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/linuxgo", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "be an engineer", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/56d78d29dd19ac9bb3a1b5206ccf9223?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/56d78d29dd19ac9bb3a1b5206ccf9223?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/56d78d29dd19ac9bb3a1b5206ccf9223?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1604655543, "last_modified": 1664435306}, "last_reply_by": "xinh", "last_touched": 1664551356, "title": "为什么 Linux 现在对硬件的需求和 windows 对硬件的需求差别越来越大", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/884049", "created": 1664524393, "deleted": 0, "content": "windows 一直以来随着版本升级，对硬件的需求是一路上升，现在 4G 内存跑个 windows10 开个机一半多内存没了，再开个浏览器或者 office 之类的，内存就告急。\r\n反观 linux ，现在的桌面版本却是越做越小巧，很多桌面如 xfce ，openbox ，lxqt 等开机后内存占用甚至都不到 1G ，我试过再开个 freecad 的 3d 图，内存也就用了 2G 多点，但是 windows10 下基本就到 3.5G 了\r\n另外硬盘占用也是，windows 刚装完系统基本就是 20G 起跳，而 linux 桌面一般装完后只有 10G 不到，老电脑跑不动 windows 的，装了 linux 却可以流畅运行，而且 linux 这些年桌面的效果也越来越漂亮了，并不比 windows10 差\r\n难道 M$技术开始走下坡路了？", "content_rendered": "windows 一直以来随着版本升级，对硬件的需求是一路上升，现在 4G 内存跑个 windows10 开个机一半多内存没了，再开个浏览器或者 office 之类的，内存就告急。<br />反观 linux ，现在的桌面版本却是越做越小巧，很多桌面如 xfce ，openbox ，lxqt 等开机后内存占用甚至都不到 1G ，我试过再开个 freecad 的 3d 图，内存也就用了 2G 多点，但是 windows10 下基本就到 3.5G 了<br />另外硬盘占用也是，windows 刚装完系统基本就是 20G 起跳，而 linux 桌面一般装完后只有 10G 不到，老电脑跑不动 windows 的，装了 linux 却可以流畅运行，而且 linux 这些年桌面的效果也越来越漂亮了，并不比 windows10 差<br />难道 M$技术开始走下坡路了？", "last_modified": 1664524393, "replies": 92, "id": 884049}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_large.png?m=1648291973", "name": "reading", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_normal.png?m=1648291973", "title": "阅读", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/reading", "topics": 519, "footer": "", "header": "少上网，多读书", "title_alternative": "Reading", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_mini.png?m=1648291973", "stars": 1302, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 111, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 240367, "username": "buttenkill", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/buttenkill", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1f75679f20a9dacea8329c8afef8ec55?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1f75679f20a9dacea8329c8afef8ec55?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1f75679f20a9dacea8329c8afef8ec55?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1500046824, "last_modified": 1661500087}, "last_reply_by": "benedict00", "last_touched": 1664579203, "title": "你最近买的纸质书是什么", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/884039", "created": 1664522846, "deleted": 0, "content": "我最近买的是“小径分岔的花园”上海译文出版社，年初淘宝促销买的，不到 8 块钱。\r\n\r\n这也大概会是我最后一次买纸质书了。", "content_rendered": "<p>我最近买的是“小径分岔的花园”上海译文出版社，年初淘宝促销买的，不到 8 块钱。</p>\n<p>这也大概会是我最后一次买纸质书了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1664522876, "replies": 87, "id": 884039}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 190809, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3571, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 456146, "username": "excitedXXX", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/excitedXXX", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3dd8/cef7/456146_mini.png?m=1661482160", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3dd8/cef7/456146_normal.png?m=1661482160", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3dd8/cef7/456146_large.png?m=1661482160", "created": 1574943267, "last_modified": 1661482160}, "last_reply_by": "binux", "last_touched": 1664566820, "title": "内推前同事入职现公司应该谁请谁吃饭？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/883977", "created": 1664507105, "deleted": 0, "content": "前言：前公司 996 五险一金最低标准苦不堪言离职，现公司 965 五险一金最高基本不加班。我拿到了内推奖励其他同事觉得我应该请他吃饭，但是我却觉得我带他来了更好的公司不应该是他请我吃饭吗。", "content_rendered": "前言：前公司 996 五险一金最低标准苦不堪言离职，现公司 965 五险一金最高基本不加班。我拿到了内推奖励其他同事觉得我应该请他吃饭，但是我却觉得我带他来了更好的公司不应该是他请我吃饭吗。", "last_modified": 1664507187, "replies": 80, "id": 883977}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 18529, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 4548, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 565360, "username": "watkin1994", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/watkin1994", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/79e6b40560287b5050344564f4090f03?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/79e6b40560287b5050344564f4090f03?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/79e6b40560287b5050344564f4090f03?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1639446495, "last_modified": 1664518414}, "last_reply_by": "wonderfulcxm", "last_touched": 1664568866, "title": "写了一个匹配交友的公众号，运营了一周，结果..", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/884029", "created": 1664519613, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，之前花了很多精力去开发的一个能提供匹配功能的公众号（类似一周 cp ，三天情侣那种形式），开始时候感觉只要做出来，推广方面啥的都会很顺利。结果做出来了，加了一大堆的 QQ 群，从微信大量转发到 Q 群上面，中间也去了一些论坛发帖，结果最后才 10 来个人关注。参加活动的更少了，只有 7 个。而且最大的问题是没有女用户，报名活动的几乎全是男性。\r\n\r\n***总结***\r\n\r\n经过这件事感觉运营是个重活，特别是对程序员来讲，是特别耗费心力的。现在纠结这个项目要不要放弃掉。或者下次个人要开发新的项目时要选择重技术的，轻运营的。或者大家有没有什么好的建议。", "content_rendered": "<p>如题，之前花了很多精力去开发的一个能提供匹配功能的公众号（类似一周 cp ，三天情侣那种形式），开始时候感觉只要做出来，推广方面啥的都会很顺利。结果做出来了，加了一大堆的 QQ 群，从微信大量转发到 Q 群上面，中间也去了一些论坛发帖，结果最后才 10 来个人关注。参加活动的更少了，只有 7 个。而且最大的问题是没有女用户，报名活动的几乎全是男性。</p>\n<p><em><strong>总结</strong></em></p>\n<p>经过这件事感觉运营是个重活，特别是对程序员来讲，是特别耗费心力的。现在纠结这个项目要不要放弃掉。或者下次个人要开发新的项目时要选择重技术的，轻运营的。或者大家有没有什么好的建议。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1664519613, "replies": 80, "id": 884029}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 9746, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5157, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 514602, "username": "xiamy1314", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiamy1314", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fdea/4f6a/514602_mini.png?m=1664502193", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fdea/4f6a/514602_normal.png?m=1664502193", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fdea/4f6a/514602_large.png?m=1664502193", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fdea/4f6a/514602_xlarge.png?m=1664502193", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fdea/4f6a/514602_xlarge.png?m=1664502193", "created": 1603681172, "last_modified": 1664502193}, "last_reply_by": "JensenQian", "last_touched": 1664539240, "title": "买手机求助。", "url": "https://ww